  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.poster.avif?t=1736964249\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.webm?t=1736964249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.mp4?t=1736964249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your last objective: KILL</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An endless horde of Démons flood in as you struggle to survive. Too angry to die, Shogun raises hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHOGUN is an arcade style shooter that emphasizes running and gunning to stay alive. Rip through waves of increasingly difficult enemies hell-bent on your doom by shooting, looting, and eluding a bullet hell of cartoonish horror. Refuse death, explode with burning rage, and tear asunder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the games that founded the fps genre, SHOGUN was created to give homage to the demon slaying experience in a bite sized form.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.poster.avif?t=1736964249\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.webm?t=1736964249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010160/extras/add903ee7c34dceae6695ece4eae2f5a.mp4?t=1736964249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your last objective: KILL</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An endless horde of Démons flood in as you struggle to survive. Too angry to die, Shogun raises hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SHOGUN is an arcade style shooter that emphasizes running and gunning to stay alive. Rip through waves of increasingly difficult enemies hell-bent on your doom by shooting, looting, and eluding a bullet hell of cartoonish horror. Refuse death, explode with burning rage, and tear asunder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the games that founded the fps genre, SHOGUN was created to give homage to the demon slaying experience in a bite sized form.</p>",
